design:
**Files**:
- `tools/proto/api/v1/auth.proto` (new) — AuthService: Login, RefreshToken
- `tools/proto/api/v1/test.proto` (new) — TestService: RunTestSuite, GetTestStatus, GetTestResult, ListTestRuns
- `tools/proto/api/v1/topology.proto` (new) — TopologyService: ValidateTopology
- `tools/proto/api/v1/settings.proto` (new) — SettingsService: GetSettings, UpdateSettings
- `tools/proto/api/v1/execution.proto` (new) — ExecutionService: StreamWorkflowGraph (server stream)
- `tools/proto/easyp.yaml` (modify) — добавить connect-go и connect-es плагины по образцу 808baas

**Approach**:
1. Создать api/v1/ package в tools/proto/
2. AuthService:
   - Login(LoginRequest{username,password}) → LoginResponse{access_token,refresh_token,expires_at}
   - RefreshToken(RefreshTokenRequest{refresh_token}) → RefreshTokenResponse{access_token,refresh_token,expires_at}
3. TestService:
   - RunTestSuite(RunTestSuiteRequest{test_suite}) → RunTestSuiteResponse{run_id}
   - GetTestStatus(GetTestStatusRequest{run_id}) → GetTestStatusResponse{status,current_step,progress}
   - GetTestResult(GetTestResultRequest{run_id}) → GetTestResultResponse{result}
   - ListTestRuns(ListTestRunsRequest{page_size,page_token}) → ListTestRunsResponse{runs,next_page_token}
4. TopologyService:
   - ValidateTopology(ValidateTopologyRequest{test_suite}) → ValidateTopologyResponse{errors[]={field_path,severity,message}}
5. SettingsService:
   - GetSettings(GetSettingsRequest) → GetSettingsResponse{settings}
   - UpdateSettings(UpdateSettingsRequest{settings}) → UpdateSettingsResponse{settings}
6. ExecutionService:
   - StreamWorkflowGraph(StreamWorkflowGraphRequest{run_id}) → stream StreamWorkflowGraphResponse{graph}
7. Добавить connect-go генератор в easyp.yaml
8. Запустить easyp generate, проверить что Go и TS код создан

**Verification**: easyp generate успешно + go build ./... + ls web/src/proto/api/
